From 178d3654c0fe621c9317e97b27076a5bbb20cc11 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: =?UTF-8?q?Bartek=20Iwa=C5=84czuk?= <biwanczuk@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 7 May 2026 12:09:50 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] perf(ext/node): convert more polyfills to lazy-loaded JS

Convert 3 `node:*` modules from eagerly-loaded ESM to lazy-loaded IIFE
scripts with thin ESM wrappers: `node:console`, `node:readline`,
`node:sqlite`.

Update import sites in `01_require.js`, `repl.ts`, `http2.ts`, and
`internal/fs/handle.ts` to use `core.loadExtScript()` instead of ESM
imports.
---
