Date: Thu, 7 May 2026 13:25:50 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] fix: drop console and readline - their deps are in esm,
 not lazy_loaded_js

loadExtScript() can only resolve scripts from the lazy_loaded_js
registry. _readline.mjs and internal/console/constructor.mjs are
still in the esm section, so the snapshot build fails.

Keep only node:sqlite whose deps (internal/util/types.ts,
ext:deno_web/00_url.js) are already in lazy_loaded_js.
